data.description: Welcome to the highly desirable Stadium Condominiums! 198 Locust St Unit 701, come fall in love with this beautifully renovated penthouse corner unit. The entry foyer has three closets, one of which contains your newer in-unit laundry. The large dining/ living room combo room offers a large space for a variety of configurations. California spit, you have one bedroom on each side of the unit, offering privacy. The primary bedroom is spacious & has a generous walk-in closet & an ensuite bathroom with stand-up, walk-in shower. The second bedroom is sizable with a large double-door closet. The kitchen was recently remodeled with stylish tile backsplash & floors & granite countertops, as well as an added kitchen island, offering the room more storage, counter space, & seating. With a rec room, landscaped common outdoor space, and an in-ground pool, all professionally maintained, experience ultimate comfort! Schedule your private showings today.
